<p>&nbsp;</p>
<hr style="clear: both;" />
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 18px;"><a href="http://www.brookings.edu/research/reports/2013/07/vital-statistics-congress-staff-operating-expenses-mann-ornstein"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px;">Chapter 5: Congressional Staff and Operating Expenses</span></strong></a></span></strong></p>
<p><a href="http://www.brookings.edu/research/reports/2013/07/vital-statistics-congress-staff-operating-expenses-mann-ornstein"><img style="width: 90px; float: left; height: 90px;  margin-right: 10px;border: 0px solid;" alt="Expenses" src="http://www.brookings.edu/~/media/Multimedia/Interactives/2013/stats/icons/stats_icons06.jpg" /></a>Chapter 5 enumerates the size of congressional staff&mdash;for individual members as well as for committees&mdash;and the appropriations for member offices.<br />
&nbsp;</p>
<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold;"><img style="width: 17px; height: 20px;" alt="PDF" src="http://www.brookings.edu/~/media/General Assets/Icons/pdf_icon.jpg" />&nbsp;<a href="http://www.brookings.edu/~/media/Research/Files/Reports/2013/07/vital statistics congress mann ornstein/Vital Statistics Chapter 5  Congressional Staff and Operating Expenses.pdf" target="_blank">Download Chapter 5 in PDF &raquo;</a></span> <br />
